<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.2">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2025-01-15T21:13:59-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Hermosawave Photography</title><subtitle>A series of daily landscape photographs by Daniel Sofer, 20 years running.</subtitle><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><entry><title type="html">Low Tide Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250114/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Low Tide Sunset" /><published>2025-01-14T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2025-01-14T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/low-tide</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250114/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
    Ripples in the water under the Hermosa Beach Pier at low tide.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">干潮時の夕日</span>

ハーモサビーチの桟橋の下、干潮時の浜辺に広がる波紋。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Hermosa Pier" /><category term="Low Tide" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Ripples in the water under the Hermosa Beach Pier at low tide.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00650-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00650-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Pier Reflection</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250113/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Pier Reflection" /><published>2025-01-13T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2025-01-13T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/pier-reflection</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250113/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The setting sun shines through the Hermosa Beach Pier, which is reflected on the beach at low tide.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">桟橋の反射</span>

夕日がハーモサビーチの桟橋を通して輝き、その反射光が干潮時にビーチに映し出されます。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Hermosa Pier" /><category term="Low Tide" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The setting sun shines through the Hermosa Beach Pier, which is reflected on the beach at low tide.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00609.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00609.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Pt. Vicente Lighthouse</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250111/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Pt. Vicente Lighthouse" /><published>2025-01-11T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2025-01-11T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/lighthouse</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250111/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Once a month, the 100 year old <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Point_Vicente_Lighthouse" target="_blank">Point Vicente Lighthouse</a> grounds are opened and visitors can walk around the lighthouse area. Still can't go in the lighthouse, unfortunately.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ポイント・ビセンテ灯台</span>

100年の歴史を持つポイント・ビセンテ灯台の敷地は、月に一度一般公開され、来訪者は灯台の周辺を散策することができます。残念ながら、灯台の中に入ることはできません。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Lighthouses" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Once a month, the 100 year old Point Vicente Lighthouse grounds are opened and visitors can walk around the lighthouse area. Still can't go in the lighthouse, unfortunately.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00536_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00536_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Fire Red Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250108/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Fire Red Sunset" /><published>2025-01-08T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2025-01-08T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/vicente-bluffs</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250108/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
    Smoke from the Los Angeles wildfires causing a red sunset tonight. Looking through reeds at the Vicente Bluffs in Rancho Palos Verdes.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ファイヤーレッドの夕焼け</span>

ロサンゼルス山火事による煙が、今夜の夕焼けを赤く染めている。ランチョ・パロス・ベルデスのビセンテ断崖を葦越しに見る。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Smoke from the Los Angeles wildfires causing a red sunset tonight. Looking through reeds at the Vicente Bluffs in Rancho Palos Verdes.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00502-3.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00502-3.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Fire Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250107/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Fire Sunset" /><published>2025-01-07T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2025-01-07T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/herondo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250107/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
    Smoke from a large fire in Pacific Palisades creates a stripe across the sky in the South Bay.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">火事夕焼け</span>
  パシフィック・パリセーズで発生した大規模火災の煙が、サウスベイの空に縞模様を描いている。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Smoke from a large fire in Pacific Palisades creates a stripe across the sky in the South Bay.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00471.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00471.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Noble Park</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250106/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Noble Park" /><published>2025-01-06T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2025-01-06T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/noble-park</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250106/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
    Benches at Hermosa’s park by the beach, along the Strand.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ノーブル・パーク</span>
    ハーモサのビーチ沿いにある公園のベンチ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Parks" /><category term="Strand" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Benches at Hermosa’s park by the beach, along the Strand.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00429_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00429_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Tower Telescope</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250105/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Tower Telescope" /><published>2025-01-05T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2025-01-05T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/catalina</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250105/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
    On the Terranea Trail, looking south at Catalina Island. A telescope is available to take a closer look at the view.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">タワー望遠鏡</span>
    テラネア・トレイルから南にカタリナ島を望む。望遠鏡が用意されており、景色を間近に眺めることができる。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Views" /><category term="Dusk" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[On the Terranea Trail, looking south at Catalina Island. A telescope is available to take a closer look at the view.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00308.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_A7R00308.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hazy Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250103/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hazy Sunset" /><published>2025-01-03T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2025-01-03T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/dtla</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250103/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A hazy sunset, shot from the top of the Wilshire Grand building in downtown LA.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">霞んだ夕焼け</span>
LAのダウンタウンにあるウィルシェアグランドビルの屋上から撮影した、霞んだ夕焼け。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Los Angeles" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A hazy sunset, shot from the top of the Wilshire Grand building in downtown LA.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_IMG_2352_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_IMG_2352_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">End of the Year</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241231/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="End of the Year" /><published>2024-12-31T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-31T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nyepier</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241231/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
