太陽がかすかな雲の列とともに沈む、トパーズ・ストリートの桟橋とライフガードの塔の向こうに。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The sun sets alongside a trail of wispy clouds, beyond the Topaz St. Jetty and lifeguard tower.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R00210-HDR-brighter.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R00210-HDR-brighter.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>